## Current `global.css` Design System

### Theme tokens (`@theme`)

| Token | Value | Usage |
|-------|-------|-------|
| `--color-white` | `#FDFDF9` | Background |
| `--color-black` | `#0E0E0E` | Text, shadows |
| `--color-brand` | `#5F46E7` | Purple accent |
| `--color-brand-light` | `#C9C3FF` | Light purple, labels |
| `--color-grey` | `#E6E7F2` | Grid lines, borders |
| `--font-heading` | Space Mono | Headings |
| `--font-body` | Plus Jakarta Sans | Body text |
| `--radius-canvas` | `40px` | Main canvas radius |
| `--spacing-canvas-x` | `45px` | Canvas horizontal gutter |
| `--spacing-canvas-top` | `48px` | Canvas top gutter |

### Utility classes

| Utility | Purpose | GPU cost |
|---------|---------|----------|
| `sandbox-grid-bg` | Fixed skewed background grid (body level) | Medium (1 element, has `will-change`) |
| `base-card-shadow` | Inner + drop shadow on cards | Low (box-shadow, no filter) |
| `base-card-blur` | **No-op** (was 0.5px blur) | None |
| `base-card-grid` | Skewed grid inside each card (::before) | Medium (has `will-change`) |
| `img-drop-shadow` | Drop shadow on images | Low |
| `label-effects` | Inner + drop shadow on labels | Low |
| `canvas-shadow` | Drop shadow on the main canvas | Low |
| `canvas-backdrop-blur` | 0.9px backdrop blur on canvas | Low |
| `canvas-gradient` | Brand → grey → brand-light diagonal | None |
| `canvas-noise-overlay` | SVG noise + overlay blend (isolated) | Low (1 element, `isolation: isolate`) |
| `card-grid` | Secondary brand-light square grid | Low |

